table multiprocessing_extra70.TimeoutError_hierarchy:
  description: "multiprocessing TimeoutError __name__/__module__/__bases__ checks in mpann70 namespace — wave 238 theme: TimeoutError exception hierarchy; TimeoutError.__name__=='TimeoutError'; TimeoutError.__module__=='multiprocessing.context'; TimeoutError.__bases__[0].__name__=='ProcessError' (multiprocessing.TimeoutError is distinct from built-in TimeoutError and inherits from ProcessError); NEW in extra70: first module and bases checks for multiprocessing.TimeoutError in the mpann70 namespace; verified with Python 3.14.3"
  kind: python_call_eq
