invariant multiprocessing_extra70.Queue_class_name_method:
  description: "multiprocessing.Queue.__class__.__name__.__eq__('method') returns True — multiprocessing.Queue is a context-bound method (factory function); its __class__.__name__ is 'method'; NEW in extra70: first standalone __class__.__name__ invariant for Queue in the mpann70 namespace; wave 238 first factory type invariant for Queue; verified with Python 3.14.3"
